          <span class="group-[.is-stuck]/surface:blur-none group-[.is-stuck]/surface:opacity-100 group-[.is-stuck]/surface:delay-150 group-[.is-stuck]/surface:block opacity-0 transition-all hidden blur-sm transition-discrete duration-500 ease-out">Get a demo</span>
